blog.name: wiggybe
blog.title: WiggyBe
blog.description:
Hi, I'm Wiggy!
I draw stuff and sometimes people like it.
I'm an animator and illustrator from the UK who likes to draw cartoons.
This is my blog, where I upload personal artwork that doesn't make it to my website, like sketches, silly comics and some fanart, and I share fun, cool and interesting things I like from others.
-To see only my own posts and artwork go to the 'My Art & Posts' at the top of the page.
-And to see only the things I like that I've reblogged from others go to 'Reblogged stuff.'
Enjoy your stay!
